title: GoEat - Food on the go made easy by Joseph Joseph
description:
GoEat is a range of innovative products that are designed to make eating homemade food on the go easy and convenient.

With GoEat you eliminate the need to carry around multiple food containers, and all the elements of your lunch are kept safe and separate until you’re ready to combine them.

When lunch is finished, each item then compacts down to save space in your bag for the journey home.

The range comprises a variety of containers with clever leak-proof silicone lids that are perfect for sandwiches, salads, soups or snacks plus a compact stainless-steel cutlery set.
